# Calendar API Tests

### Get all categories
GET {{ClupApi_HostAddress}}/api/calendar/categories
Accept: application/json

###

### Get events by date range (December 2024)
GET {{ClupApi_HostAddress}}/api/calendar/events?startDate=2024-12-01&endDate=2024-12-31
Accept: application/json

###

### Get events by date range (January 2025)
GET {{ClupApi_HostAddress}}/api/calendar/events?startDate=2025-01-01&endDate=2025-01-31
Accept: application/json

###

### Get daily events (today)
GET {{ClupApi_HostAddress}}/api/calendar/events/daily?date=2024-12-03
Accept: application/json

###

### Test validation - Invalid date range (startDate > endDate)
GET {{ClupApi_HostAddress}}/api/calendar/events?startDate=2024-12-31&endDate=2024-12-01
Accept: application/json

###

### Test validation - Too large date range (> 3 months)
GET {{ClupApi_HostAddress}}/api/calendar/events?startDate=2024-01-01&endDate=2024-12-31
Accept: application/json

